<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>fibrous tissue only</div><div><br/></div><div>Microscopic description:</div><div>Section shows presence of fibrous wall of the cystic lesion. There is no epithelial lining and cannot make a definite diagnosis.</div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
