<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>fistula, consistent with first branchial cleft anomaly.</div><div><br/></div><div>Microscopic description:</div><div>Section shows fistulous tracts lined by squamous and ciliated respiratory-type epithelium, focally containing keratin materials. Adnexal structures<span>    </span></div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
