    </note-attributes>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>Mucous retention cyst</div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
  <note>
    <title>未命名記事</title>
    <created>20180705T071554Z</created>
    <updated>20230713T063557Z</updated>
    <note-attributes>
      <author>Elaine huang</author>
      <source>desktop.win</source>
      <source-application>evernote.win32</source-application>
    </note-attributes>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div><span style="font-family: gotham, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12px;">Nasal polyp</span></span></div><div><br/></div><div><span style="font-family: gotham;"><span style="font-size: 9pt;">Microscopic description:</span></span></div><div><span style="font-family: gotham;"><span style="font-size: 9pt;">The polyp is lined by respiratory epithelium exhibiting focal squamous metaplasia and thickening of the basement membrane. The underlying stroma appears loose and mucoid, with intact mucous glands and infiltrate of neutrophils, lymphocytes and mild/moderate/numerous eosinophils. No malignancy is observed.</span></span></div><div><br/></div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
  <note>
    <title>Nasoalveolar cyst (ENT-NA)</title>
    <created>20161115T051803Z</created>
    <updated>20250226T052553Z</updated>
    <note-attributes>
      <author>Elaine huang</author>
    </note-attributes>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>nasoalveolar cyst.</div><div><br/></div><div>Microscopic description:</div><div>The cyst is lined by respiratory epithelium and pseudostratified columnar epithelium.</div><div>Chronic inflammatory cells are seen in the surrounding fibrovascular stroma.</div><div><br/></div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
  <note>
    <title>未命名記事</title>
    <created>20230120T031527Z</created>
    <updated>20230120T032016Z</updated>
